@startuml audio_popup_sync_to_clu_duplicate_guard_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Audio Popup Sync To CLU Duplicate Guard Signal Flow\n(audio focus + popup + sync state + cluster warning -> CLU duplicate-guarded warning text)

participant "Cluster warning bus" as Warn #F4F7FB
participant "Popup / audio / sync buses" as Aux #E8F0FE
participant "CLU\ncluster-render owner" as CLU #E8F7E8
participant "Cluster/Core seams" as CluBus #FFF4CC
participant "Observers /\ncluster readers" as Obs #FFF4CC

== CLU Inputs ==

Warn -> CLU : frmClusterWarningMsg\nWarningTextCode
Aux -> CLU : frmHmiPopupStateMsg / frmAudioFocusMsg /\nfrmSpeechTtsStateMsg / frmClusterSyncStateMsg
activate CLU
CLU -> CLU : applyDisplayPolicy(rawCode)
CLU -> CLU : applyRobustPolicy(code)\nusing popup/audio/tts/sync/backbone alert state
CLU -> CLU : if same warning repeats within 1000 ms\nthen duplicatePopupGuard remains active
CLU -> CLU : if code changes then pushHistory() /\nrespondHistoryQuery()
note right of CLU
Representative gating inputs
- WarningTextCode
- PopupPriority / PopupActive
- AudioFocusOwner / AudioDuckingLvl
- TtsState
- ClusterSyncState / ClusterSyncAge
end note

== CLU Publish ==

CLU -> CluBus : Cluster::warningTextCode
CLU -> CluBus : CoreState::duplicatePopupGuard /\nclusterNotifType / clusterNotifPrio
note right of CLU
Representative outputs
- warningTextCode
- duplicatePopupGuard
- clusterNotifType
- clusterNotifPrio
end note

== Downstream Visibility ==

CluBus -> Obs : cluster text visibility /\nduplicate-popup guard observers
deactivate CLU

note over Warn, Obs
Representative runtime chain
1. Cluster warning and auxiliary popup/audio/sync context reach CLU
2. CLU applies robust policy and duplicate-popup suppression
3. CLU updates warning text and duplicate guard seams
4. Cluster observers read the guarded warning presentation state
end note

@enduml
